@startuml
' Diagram: F11 - State machine cua YeuCauThanhToan (yeu cau thanh toan goi app)
' Status: VERIFIED
' Baseline: branch master, current worktree @ HEAD 8ed8643
' Source:
' - VinhKhanhTour.API/Models/YeuCauThanhToan.cs: TrangThai = "cho_duyet" | "da_duyet" | "tu_choi"
' - VinhKhanhTour.API/Controllers/SubscriptionController.cs: CreateRequest(), GetRequestStatus()
' - VinhKhanhTour.CMS/Pages/DuyetThanhToan/Index.cshtml.cs: OnPostApproveAsync(), OnPostRejectAsync()
' - VinhKhanhTourDemo/PaymentPage.xaml.cs: OnDaChuyenKhoanClicked()
' - VinhKhanhTourDemo/PaymentStatusPage.xaml.cs: PollStatusAsync(), ShowSuccess(), ShowRejected()
' Note: Day la state diagram cua mot YeuCauThanhToan tu khi tao den khi ket thuc.
' Note: Cot DB: trangthai (cho_duyet/da_duyet/tu_choi), ngaytao, ngayduyet, ghichu_admin.
' Note: Trang thai cuoi (da_duyet, tu_choi) la terminal — khong co transition reopen trong code hien tai.
' Note: F08 khong co transaction guard giua 2 admin Approve dong thoi (rui ro RISK-014/concurrency); nut Approve chi check "TrangThai != cho_duyet" sau khi load, KHONG dung row lock.
title F11 - State machine: YeuCauThanhToan

[*] --> cho_duyet : Khach POST /api/subscription/request\n(tao YeuCauThanhToan, NgayTao=now)

state cho_duyet {
  cho_duyet : entry / TrangThai = "cho_duyet"
  cho_duyet : entry / NgayTao = UtcNow
  cho_duyet : NgayDuyet = null
  cho_duyet : GhiChuAdmin = null
  cho_duyet : --
  cho_duyet : App polling moi 10 giay:
  cho_duyet :   GET /api/subscription/request/{yeuCauId}
  cho_duyet : Admin thay trong CMS:
  cho_duyet :   /DuyetThanhToan?tab=cho_duyet
  cho_duyet :   PendingSnapshot polling
}

cho_duyet --> da_duyet : Admin POST OnPostApproveAsync(yeuCauId)\n[load + check TrangThai == cho_duyet]\n/ Tao DangKyApp moi (gia han noi tiep)\n/ TrangThai = "da_duyet"\n/ NgayDuyet = UtcNow

cho_duyet --> tu_choi : Admin POST OnPostRejectAsync(yeuCauId, lyDo)\n[load + check TrangThai == cho_duyet]\n/ TrangThai = "tu_choi"\n/ NgayDuyet = UtcNow\n/ GhiChuAdmin = lyDo

state da_duyet {
  da_duyet : entry / TrangThai = "da_duyet"
  da_duyet : entry / NgayDuyet = UtcNow
  da_duyet : entry / Tao DangKyApp(MaThietBi, LoaiGoi, NgayBatDau, NgayHetHan)
  da_duyet : entry / Neu da co goi con han:\n  NgayBatDau = NgayHetHan cua goi cu\n  (gia han noi tiep, khong mat ngay)
  da_duyet : entry / Neu het han / chua co:\n  NgayBatDau = UtcNow
  da_duyet : --
  da_duyet : App ShowSuccess() + Preferences.Set(sub_ngay_het_han)
  da_duyet : Polling dung lai (PollCts.Cancel())
}

state tu_choi {
  tu_choi : entry / TrangThai = "tu_choi"
  tu_choi : entry / NgayDuyet = UtcNow
  tu_choi : entry / GhiChuAdmin = lyDo
  tu_choi : --
  tu_choi : App ShowRejected(lyDo)
  tu_choi : User co the bam "Thu lai":
  tu_choi :   PopModalAsync() → quay lai PaymentPage
  tu_choi :   tao YeuCauThanhToan MOI (Id khac)
  tu_choi : Polling dung lai (PollCts.Cancel())
}

da_duyet --> [*]
tu_choi --> [*]

note bottom of cho_duyet
  Edge case chua xu ly trong code (rui ro RISK):
  - 2 admin cung Approve 1 yeu cau → ca 2 deu tao DangKyApp moi (race).
    Khac phuc: them transaction + select for update,
    hoac unique constraint tren (YeuCauId).
  - Polling 404/500 → app im lang vong lap mai
    (RISK-013): can them backoff + max retry.
  - Khach "Thu lai" sau tu_choi tao request moi
    nhung KHONG xoa request cu → DB co the dem
    nhieu ban "tu_choi" cho cung 1 thiet bi.
end note
@enduml
